night after night.

19:13.447 --> 19:15.615
I-I have no idea--

19:15.649 --> 19:17.317
Virginia: She's blond.

19:17.351 --> 19:21.888
26 years old, 5'7",
average-sized breasts,

19:21.923 --> 19:23.623
typical areolae...

19:23.657 --> 19:25.758
Austin:
Everyone has typical areolae!

19:25.793 --> 19:27.928
Virginia: You were paired
with her on March 10th,

19:27.962 --> 19:30.596
for one episode
of missionary coitus

19:30.631 --> 19:35.301
lasting 6 minutes, 18 seconds.

19:35.335 --> 19:36.936
Austin: This is a joke.

19:36.970 --> 19:39.439
[ Breathing heavily ]

19:39.473 --> 19:41.741
What about all the other guys
you-- you paired her with?

19:41.775 --> 19:43.543
I mean, I was paired up
with maybe a dozen.

19:43.577 --> 19:47.112
Virginia: She only had one partner
in the study and no boyfriend, so...

19:47.147 --> 19:49.815
she filled out
a detailed sexual history.

19:49.849 --> 19:52.584
Austin: Look, this is
your problem, not mine, okay?

19:52.618 --> 19:56.922
It's your study. I was
basically... an organ donor.

19:56.957 --> 19:58.357
And if she didn't use
protection--

19:58.391 --> 20:00.326
Virginia:
Her diaphragm failed.

20:00.360 --> 20:03.161
It happens more often
than you'd think.

20:05.565 --> 20:08.667
Austin:
6 minutes and 18 seconds?

20:11.804 --> 20:15.373
What does she want from me?
I mean, she want money?

20:15.407 --> 20:16.875
Elise balances our checkbook.

20:16.909 --> 20:18.710
She's like a--
like a bloodhound.

20:18.744 --> 20:20.445
Virginia:
I have no idea what she wants.

20:20.479 --> 20:21.745
And I'm not saying

20:21.780 --> 20:24.449
