What the hell is going on?

21:12.830 --> 21:14.664
Telephone's
ringing off the hook.

21:14.698 --> 21:16.298
Jane: Sorry, Dr. Masters.

21:16.333 --> 21:20.202
I'm fourth-floor hall Marshall
for civil defense.

21:20.237 --> 21:22.171
William: When Khrushchev
pushes the button,

21:22.205 --> 21:23.472
