21:23.507 --> 21:25.408
Until then,
you're still my secretary.

21:31.814 --> 21:34.130
[ Air-raid siren blaring ] _

21:37.120 --> 21:40.022
Man: Go to your stations!
Get down!

21:40.057 --> 21:43.291
[ Indistinct talking ]

21:45.428 --> 21:48.730
Gwynne: Mrs. Johnson!
We are under attack!

21:48.765 --> 21:52.067
