22:32.440 --> 22:34.608
Lillian:
They included a check.

22:37.745 --> 22:38.945
Virginia: $600?

22:38.980 --> 22:41.848
Lillian: Nearly as much
as the hospital spent

22:41.882 --> 22:45.085
