for its civil defense program.

22:45.120 --> 22:48.154
Not enough for lab equipment
or a proper staff.

22:48.188 --> 22:49.789
It'll pay for mimeographs

22:49.824 --> 22:54.928
and the hiring of a secretary,
at minimum wage.

22:54.962 --> 22:57.964
Virginia: Well,
Rome wasn't built in a day.

22:57.999 --> 23:00.333
Neither were outreach clinics.

23:00.367 --> 23:02.368
You'll get it funded,
eventually.

23:02.402 --> 23:04.337
Lillian:
"Eventually" isn't good enough.

23:04.371 --> 23:06.272
I wasted three months
on that proposal,

23:06.306 --> 23:08.807
laying groundwork, sucking up
to the administration...

23:08.842 --> 23:11.744
Virginia: [ Chuckling ]

23:11.778 --> 23:14.380
