for men and women.

23:32.431 --> 23:35.167
Trust me, a little charm
goes a long way.

23:35.201 --> 23:38.203
Lillian: Pearls of wisdom
from the steno pool.

23:38.237 --> 23:39.404
Virginia: Okay.

23:39.438 --> 23:43.107
