with your hands over your head.

24:46.870 --> 24:48.338
Austin:
I'll take my chances.

24:48.372 --> 24:51.107
[ Blaring continues ]

25:10.227 --> 25:11.560
William:
What the hell are you doing?

25:13.363 --> 25:17.031
Pratt: Air-raid siren--
means nuclear attack.

25:17.066 --> 25:19.934
William:
The attack is a simulation--

25:19.969 --> 25:22.070
unlike Mrs. Gallagher's
fibroids,

25:22.104 --> 25:24.539
- which, I assure you, are real.
- Austin: Bill!

25:24.574 --> 25:26.074
