if I'm protected in this thing.

25:28.010 --> 25:29.411
William:
Oh, God, there is no bomb!

25:29.445 --> 25:31.313
Austin:
No, not-- not the bomb.

25:31.347 --> 25:32.414
The study.

25:44.326 --> 25:47.262
[ Blaring fades,
indistinct conversations ]

25:55.771 --> 25:57.971
