circumstances.

26:17.826 --> 26:21.528
You are protected
by the forms you signed.

26:21.562 --> 26:24.597
They are, in effect, ironclad.

26:24.632 --> 26:29.402
Austin:
So, I'm all-- all clear?

26:30.471 --> 26:33.606
