27:05.037 --> 27:07.138
Pratt:
He performed one two days ago.

27:07.173 --> 27:09.341
Lang: Dr. Masters,
it's been an unusual day.

27:09.376 --> 27:10.743
We're at war with Russia.

27:10.777 --> 27:13.311
